{
  "text": "The YLL/YLD ratio in the EMR for 2015 was 19.34, almost double the global ratio of 9.77 [CITATION_1] . By country, Afghanistan had the highest ratio at 50.36, and only Kuwait and Lebanon were below the global ratio at 7.50 and 6.45, respectively (Table 1) . For all age groups and countries, YLLs were the primary contributor to DALYs in terms of TI.",
